__________ __________
DEPARTMENT TOTAL - ALL FUNDS $0 $140,500
HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES, DEPARTMENT OF
Office of Behavioral Health Z199
Initiative: Provides one-time allocation for the Office of Behavioral Health to contract with
an entity to provide the required pretrial services for the new drug treatment court in
Aroostook County.
OTHER SPECIAL REVENUE FUNDS 2025-26 2026-27
All Other $0 $561,283
