__________ __________
DEPARTMENT TOTAL - ALL FUNDS $0 $561,283
PUBLIC DEFENSE SERVICES, MAINE COMMISSION ON
Maine Commission on Public Defense Services Z112
Initiative: Appropriates one-time funds to provide legal representation to participants in the
new drug treatment court in Aroostook County.
GENERAL FUND 2025-26 2026-27
All Other $0 $39,000
__________ __________
